sonarr_episodefile_episodeoverviews: Miia trains to become Kimihito's bride by throwing herself into cooking. However, she seems absent minded and burns both of her hands. She is out of sorts because she is shedding. She cries that she is useless and can't even shed by herself, but Kimihito cheers her up and offers to help her shed.
